slapt-update-notifier: slapt-update-notifier (Daemon which notifies about package updates)
slapt-update-notifier: 
slapt-update-notifier: slapt-update-notifier is a Daemon which notifies about package
slapt-update-notifier: updates.  It places an icon in the user's notification area when
slapt-update-notifier: package updates are available.
slapt-update-notifier: 
slapt-update-notifier: Cron entries are added to /etc/cron.daily and /etc/cron.hourly as
slapt-update-notifier: well as a small modification to /etc/rc.d/rc.local
